text: can we talk later? I’m in the middle of something important.
I figured. The “important thing” just liked your Instagram story.

sender: Sure. And the selfie she posted from your hoodie is “cosplay
It’s a common hoodie. Anyone could have it.
Funny. She spelled your name wrong in the caption but still got your birthdate right.
Okay that was a lucky guess.
She tagged the restaurant you took me to last week. Same table. Same booth. Same broken ketchup bottle.

text: the bottle has our initials carved into it.
but that carving could mean anything.

sender: Yeah. “A + J forever” absolutely screams creative ambiguity.
Why are you being so dramatic?
But your mom just DM’d me asking why your “study partner” tagged her in a photo.
The one where she’s wearing your hoodie and your dignity.
